            <text>
                <content>
                    <paragraph align="center">○ <index type="지명">灃州</index>
                        <index type="이름">僧哲禪師</index>
                        <index type="이름">哲禪師</index>弟子二人</paragraph>
                    <paragraph align="center">
                        <index type="이름">僧哲</index>弟子<index type="이름">玄遊</index>者, <index type="국명">高麗國</index>人也.  隨師於<index type="국명">師子國</index>出家, 因住彼矣.</paragraph>
                </content>
